  "time_ut": 1657539464,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dad\u0db6\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0db8 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I was at home when the house was set on fire",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe said that he was staying in that house when his house was set on fire and that the only house he had was the house that was set on fire. He said this by making a special statement. He also said that it is the Hitlerite people who can destroy the houses.",
        "\"When the struggle took place on the 9th, I postponed the meetings I had and stayed at home. I received a message from the police asking me to leave the house after the struggle in the evening.",
        "My wife and I left. This house caught fire while I was there. The only house I had in Sri Lanka and abroad has been burnt down today.",
        "My greatest treasure was the library. There are 2500 books. There are books written about the Portuguese period and the Dutch period. There are many books. Some of them have signed books like Kissinger.",
        "I can't keep these all the time. Maithri and I agreed that we should give these to the libraries. Give to Royal College. Give my oldest Portuguese Dutch books to University of Peradeniya. And there were drawings to give. Some of them are about 200 years old. They were painted when the British era came.",
        "Today I have only one left. There is a Dutch picture of King Wimaladharmasuriya meeting the Dutch ambassadors.",
        "I had Tripitaka. There were books about Buddhism. None of them. I had about 15 to 20 precious Buddha images. There is one left. I had five Buddhist monks, none of these. I have lost everything. Only Hitlerite people destroy houses like this.\""
      ],
